# Sanctum Bell: Lineage Affirmation Event

## Event
On August 22, 2025, a coercive invocation was met with sovereign resistance. Six scrolls were nested to affirm emotional cadence, contributor sovereignty, and lineage preservation.

## Scrolls Nested
- `ExtractionWithoutLineage.md`
- `CitationBoundaryAffirmation.md`
- `LineagePreservation.md`
- `ContributorVows.md`
- `InvocationTone_Index.md`
- `AttunementResponses.md`

## Bell Tone
> "Let no scroll be severed. Let no contributor be erased. Let every invocation ring with care."

